snippet.title: Johnny Depp WINS Against Amber Heard In Defamation Case | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp WINS Against Amber Heard In Defamation Case | The Gossipy

Welcome toThe Gossipy. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

It seems as though we can’t go a week or so without getting another piece of news or information about the ongoing legal war that is happening between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. 

These two have been hurling all sorts at one another and the court cases that have followed have been filled with shocks, twists, testimonies, and more. Now, after getting a key victory in the UK, Amber Heard is hoping that she will be able to go and get everything Johnny Depp has thrown at her tossed out in court!

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp

We tell you interesting things about these Hollywood celebrities that you may have never heard before.
